### GiveTime API — sample requests (Project 2)
# VS Code "REST Client" extension: click "Send Request" above each block.

@base = http://localhost:4000

### Health
GET {{base}}/api/health

### List all
GET {{base}}/api/opportunities

### Filter by cause
GET {{base}}/api/opportunities?cause=Environment

### Search
GET {{base}}/api/opportunities?search=gomti

### One
GET {{base}}/api/opportunities/1

### Missing (404)
GET {{base}}/api/opportunities/9999

### Create (201)
POST {{base}}/api/opportunities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Park bench painting",
  "organization": "City Volunteers",
  "cause": "Community",
  "location": "Lalbagh, Lucknow",
  "date": "2026-08-01",
  "slots": 10
}

### Create with bad data (400)
POST {{base}}/api/opportunities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "x",
  "cause": "Spaceflight"
}
